  "summary": {
    "zh": "英国车手，1992 年世界冠军。他驾驶威廉姆斯 FW14B 以压倒性优势夺冠，被称为「狮子」；其激进敢拼的风格赢得无数车迷。",
    "en": "British driver, 1992 world champion. He dominated in the Williams FW14B; nicknamed 'Il Leone', his aggressive style won legions of fans."
